    <name>GUI-Scale Applet</name>
    <summary>Linux GUI Wrapper Applet for the Tailscale CLI</summary>
    <description>
        <p>Linux GUI wrapper applet for the Tailscale CLI</p>
        <p>Features:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>View Tailscale connection status</li>
            <li>Enable/disable your Tailscale connection</li>
            <li>Configure Tailscale SSH and routing settings</li>
            <li>Send and receive files via Tailscale Taildrop</li>
            <li>Manage exit nodes</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            The user must first run the following command before the application will run as intended:
            <pre><code lang="bash">sudo tailscale up --operator=$USER</code></pre>
        </p>
    </description>
